   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>For the granary of the village of Theadelphia, for the crop of the 8th and 7th year, in the name of Horion and Paulos, through Ibias and . . ., twelve donkey-loads. In the 10th, 9th and 2nd year, Thoth 6th.</ab>
